title: Loring Park 1 Bed W/ Park Views from $995 Open House Mon-Fri 4pm-7pm
posting_body: ['316 Oak Grove Street', '- Studios Available from $825/month', '- 1 Bedrooms Available from $975/month', 'Parking in rear.', 'Ring #104 on callbox for leasing agent.', "Amazing walkable location in Loring Park, surrounded by parks and only a few blocks away from the Sculpture Garden, Walker Art Museum, Lakes & Legends Brewing, Eggy's, Minneapolis Convention Center, Downtown is 1/2 a mile away!", '- Each unit has updated appliances, closets, and porcelain subway tile in the bathrooms.', '- ALL utilities paid by the landlord (excluding cable/internet/phone).', '- Shared On Site Laundry & Secured Bike Storage', '- NO monthly community fees!', '- Flexible move in dates with pro-rated mid-month availability', '$40 application fee', '$875-$895 Studios', '$995-$1095 1 Bedrooms', 'Security Deposit Equals One Month of Rent', '- All utilities paid by Landlord, you just pay internet/cable tv.', '- Cats allowed with a $250 non-refundable fee.', 'There are off-street parking spots via a waiting list for the above-ground $75 a month and underground $100/ month ramps.', 'Laundry is shared and on the main level.', 'Criteria to Rent:', 'Must make 3x the monthly rent in gross income to qualify.', 'Good rental history.', 'Please refer to specifics below']
